**Trend Plot**

```python
from pytorch_cka import plot_cka_trend

# Plot diagonal (self-similarity across layers)
diagonal = torch.diag(matrix)
fig, ax = plot_cka_trend(
    diagonal,
    labels=["Self-similarity"],
    xlabel="Layer",
    ylabel="CKA Score",
)
```

