**Side-by-Side Comparison**

```python
from pytorch_cka import plot_cka_comparison

fig, axes = plot_cka_comparison(
    matrices=[matrix1, matrix2, matrix3],
    titles=["Epoch 1", "Epoch 10", "Epoch 100"],
    layers=layers,
    share_colorbar=True,
)
```

